  Chat over the aggregated profile (long context, grounding, streaming)

  Winner: Gemini 2.5 Pro. This is the use case Google has specifically invested in — long-context retrieval accuracy. With 200 video summaries (~50k tokens), the question "find the videos where the creator changed their mind about X" is
